| **OWASP Secure Code Review** | Injection (SQL, XSS, path, command), Authentication, Authorization (least privilege, horizontal escalation), input validation, PII/sensitive data | https://cheatsheetseries.owasp.org/cheatsheets/Secure_Code_Review_Cheat_Sheet.html |
