## Complexity Metrikleri
```
Cognitive Complexity (SonarQube):
├── 0-5:   Basit — kabul edilir
├── 6-10:  Orta — kabul edilir
├── 11-15: Yuksek — refactoring onerilir (SHOULD-FIX)
├── 16+:   Zorunlu refactoring (MUST-FIX)

Cyclomatic Complexity:
├── 1-10:  Kabul edilir
├── 11-15: Refactoring onerilir (SHOULD-FIX)
├── 16+:   Zorunlu refactoring (MUST-FIX)

Method Lines:         max 30 (ideal 15)
Class Lines:          max 300 (ideal 200)
Parameter Count:      max 4 (fazlasi DTO/object kullan)
Nesting Depth:        max 3 (fazlasi guard clause / early return)
Constructor/DI Count: max 5 dependency (fazlasi SRP ihlali)
```

