## Architecture Fitness Functions (CI Enforce)

> Teknolojiye ozel araclar (orn. ArchUnit, NetArchTest, eslint-plugin-boundaries) tech-pack'te tanimlanir. Asagidakiler genel ilkeler.

```
1. Katman Bagimliligi: Ic katman (Domain) dis katmana (Infrastructure) referans ETMEMELI
2. Naming Convention: Handler, Validator, Controller vb. dogru suffix/prefix kontrolu
3. Forbidden API: Proje genelinde yasakli API/patern listesi (tech-pack tanimli)
4. Test Coverage: Kritik katmanlar (Domain + Application) min coverage hedefi
5. Bundle / Build Size: Tanimlanan esik degerlerin altinda kalmali
6. Vulnerability Scan: Bilinen guvenlik acigi olan bagimlilik SIFIR
```

